<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q29_v5" title="Q29_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un negocio se vende jugo a granel y el precio es proporcional al número de botellas de 1 litro que se compran. Se registraron las siguientes ventas:</p>
    <div>
      <p>• 2 botellas: 1800 pesos.</p>
      <p>• 5 botellas: 4500 pesos.</p>
      <p>• 8 botellas: 7200 pesos.</p>
    </div>
    <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> es la cantidad de botellas compradas, ¿cuál expresión da el precio, en pesos, por <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:math> pesos, pero en el registro 2 botellas cuestan 1800 pesos. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math> no representa el precio.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <p><m:math><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El precio por botella es constante: <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1800</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4500</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>7200</m:mn><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces, para <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas, el precio es <m:math><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> pesos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>905</m:mn></m:math> pesos, pero en el registro 5 botellas cuestan 4500 pesos. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math> no representa el precio.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1800</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, esta expresión da <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1808</m:mn></m:math> pesos, pero en el registro 8 botellas cuestan 7200 pesos. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1800</m:mn></m:math> no representa el precio.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la relación proporcional</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que el precio es proporcional a la cantidad de botellas. Eso significa que el precio por botella debe ser constante.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el precio de 1 botella usando los datos</strong></p>
            <p>Con 2 botellas:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1800</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Con 5 botellas:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4500</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Con 8 botellas:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>7200</m:mn><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>En los tres casos, cada botella cuesta 900 pesos.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir la expresión para <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas</strong></p>
            <p>Si 1 botella cuesta 900 pesos, entonces <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas cuestan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con un dato del enunciado</strong></p>
            <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4500</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Coincide exactamente con el registro de 5 botellas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es <m:math><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, que corresponde a la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>